{
  "stem": "27443.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So the only Pole that I witnessed, that he was the nicest that I came across too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That he was helpful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't think that it's going to be-- that we're going to be liberated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, two days before we were liberated, there was going around a rumor in camp that they're going to dynamite the whole factory, and the Germans will dynamite the whole camp, that nobody should be a witness.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were very afraid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when they started to evacuate in the morning, the people with the first two transports, we knew that something goes on that we will not come out alive.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Either we're going to go into transport, or we'll be finished off right here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when we were taken to the bunks, they told us that we were waiting for the trains, to go on the next transport.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We never knew if we're going to be liberated, or we're going to be alive, or we-- we're going to be shot in there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or dynamite.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the Russians came there, and we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't have time to-- do something with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In fact, when the Russians came into the city, they took so much revenge on the Germans and the Poles, that the things that we witnessed, it was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They really took revenge for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "For all of us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They used to shoot them in the middle of the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to cut off their fingers, to take off their rings.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I, myself, with my girlfriend, the first two weeks, slept on the-- in the attic-- in the attic, because the Russians, when they walk-- walked in, into our camp, they kind of were very wild.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
